Babs Olusanmokun https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Babs_Olusanmokun 0 Babs Olusanmokun is a Nigerian-American actor.Olasanmokun was born in Lagos, Nigeria, and is based in New York. He is fluent in French and Portuguese, and is a jiu jitsu master.In 2017, he appeared in "Black Museum", an episode of the anthology series Black Mirror.He also appeared in the video game Max Payne 3 as Serrano: he has been both actor and voice.
